l never be touched by Hellfire.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3375,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/12\/recite-quran-too-fast\/","url_meta":{"origin":25022,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Recitation: Quran should not be recited too quickly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne has not understood the Quran if he reads it in less than three days.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2949 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064d\u0648 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0647\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26486,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/06\/06\/ahl-quran-ahl-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":25022,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Quran: People of Allah&#8217;s Book are His chosen","au